      <p>For court filing deadlines, board meeting preparations, or other time-sensitive submissions, same-day proofreading is available. Urgent pricing reflects the priority handling required. Contact us via WhatsApp for availability and quotes on urgent requests.</p>
      
      <h3>Volume Arrangements</h3>
      
      <p>Law firms, translation agencies, and businesses with regular proofreading needs benefit from volume arrangements. We offer retainer options that provide priority service and reduced per-document rates. Contact us to discuss ongoing requirements.</p>
      
